+/**
+ * lpfc_rx_monitor_create_ring - Initialize ring buffer for rx_monitor
+ * @rx_monitor: Pointer to lpfc_rx_info_monitor object
+ * @entries: Number of rx_info_entry objects to allocate in ring
+ *
